<ab>Dem hochwirdigen fürsten und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Raban, bysschof czu Speyr etc., und den
                        edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>Fridrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sche<ex>n</ex>cken</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                        Lympurg etc., und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> vom <expan>Hirshorn</expan>
<app>
<note place="inline"><expan cert="medium">de<ex>tur</ex></expan>
</note>
